snippet.title: Dreamcast Longplay - Gundam Side Story 0079: Rise From the Ashes
snippet.description:
This game, though not spectacular, is a fun treat for Gundam fans who also happen to own a Dreamcast (Hey, that describes me!).

This is the "Longplay" version of my series: the complete game sans commentary. Commentated versions of the individual levels are available on my channel.

Check out the update blog:
http://shinsen88gaming.blogspot.com
